relation: Was originally made for Cap'n Muffin's and chuggaaconroy's EarthBound: Memoirs fangame.
Tried to visualize the Enraged Fire Plug spraying water, and this is what I came up with.
An Incendiary Insect (or, Firebug, as I prefer to call them), from Mother 3's first chapter.

"You thought I was going to beg for food, didn't you ? I wouldn't do that, even though I am ever so hungry.... Give me something. Whatever it is, just give it to me. Gimme gimme. Please, give me. Why won't you give it to me ? I said please ?... I promise, I 'll give you something in return. What are you going to give me ?... Thanks a lot. To show my gratitude I 'll give you this Flea Bag. Please take it." One of the people from Reindeer in Mother 1. Made for a "We Are Starmen" contest, on deviantArt.
One of the lead EB64 characters. I later added an orange background, which I thought worked better.
